Author: SemicolonButterfly
Text: In my pantheon of ‘foods I feel ok about’ they both rank highly. Soo, the relative ranking would depend a lot on which yogurt. There’s some with higher protein that I really like (Siggi, Fage). There’s others with minimal protein and a bunch of sugar, and those get a hard pass. Tofu has a nutrition profile I feel pretty good about, but I personally have some struggles with portion control. I’ll legit nom half a block of raw tofu.
